@dark_defender: "Endgame" follows path identical to many Showcase shows - totally unreliable airing type or no capturing at all, by no one! Same thing as with in last few days often requested Lost Girl. Plain SD airing, but HDTV follows day  after! It's stupid, and for two first episodes  of Endgame I encoded first one out - as 352p, but episode 1 once again, next day, as my normal HDTV 480p. I wont do it  again - ALL future episodes would be encoded as  352p, from SD source, as one today. 

I cannot waste my time for no good reason and - make people to wait one day longer to get 20% better quality from 480p. So, who doesn't like 352p, easily can go someplace else. Sorry.
